com.tibco.tea.agent.metrics

Interface Counter

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Metric

    public interface Counter
extends Metric

    Metric for counting. The value of the Counter can be incremented or decremented.

    Examples of where a Counter can be used:
    • Number of open connections for a server
    • Number of available worker threads in a thread pool
    This class does not require external locking for thread safety.
